subject: Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Stefanie Dolson scored 14 points and Breanna Stewart added 13 to lead No. 2 Connecticut to a 63-48 victory over No. 9 Maryland in the Jimmy V Classic in Hartford.
